A serene young prince in flowing golden robes sits in deep meditation beneath an ancient sprawling Bodhi tree with heart-shaped leaves, rendered in the soft watercolor style of Studio Ghibli. Warm afternoon light filters through the canopy, casting dappled shadows across the peaceful scene. The tree's massive gnarled roots spread outward like protective arms, while tiny glowing fireflies and floating seeds drift through the air. In the background, misty mountains fade into pastel pink and orange sunset clouds. A mischievous shadowy spirit lurks at the edge of the frame, unable to approach the tranquil figure. Small woodland creatures—a deer, rabbits, and birds—gather nearby, drawn to the calm energy. The overall palette is soft greens, warm golds, and gentle earth tones, evoking childlike wonder and timeless peace.
